descriptionHtml:
This is my first mod ever, so i\'ll be happy to get criticism. 
----
The house is located near Riverwood.

The house features a new follower called Jack IronHand, and he will aid you on your adventures if you ask him.

The house also has a Mannequin, cooking pot, alchemy table and display cases on first floor.
Down the stairs is a bed, anvil, workbench, sharpening wheel, storages, a enchanting table and a tanning rack. 
The person that takes care of the house is Jack IronHand. He will aid you in your adventures if you ask him.

Basement: It has many Mannequin\'s and chest shorting.
---
To-Do

1. Make a basement for more storage and display. *Done*
2. Make a custom quest.

Please leave feedback or suggestions.
author: MrJackson
